# ============================================================
# CLOUDFLARED — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ============================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit the .env file — only .env.example
# Shared variables (TZ, PUID, PGID) come from root .env

# ============================================================
# TUNNEL CREDENTIALS
# Consumed by: cloudflared container (tunnel authentication)
#
# CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_TOKEN — found in Cloudflare Zero Trust dashboard
#   Zero Trust → Networks → Tunnels → (your tunnel) → Configure
#   → Install and run a connector → Docker → copy the token value
#   from the generated docker run command
#
# CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_ID — found in the same tunnel configuration page
#   Zero Trust → Networks → Tunnels → (your tunnel) → (the UUID
#   shown under the tunnel name)
# ============================================================
CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_TOKEN=
CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_ID=